    localMarketPara: `The San Antonio plumbing market serves a metro of Alamo Heights, Stone Oak, King William, The Pearl, and surrounding communities. CPS Energy coordinates service for water and sewer service across the metro. Texas has no statewide residential contractor license; TDLR registers mechanical and electrical trades only. San Antonio's 5 freeze-thaw cycles, 32 inches of rain, and extreme summer heat exceeding 100F for 30+ days drives specific pipe material and freeze-protection requirements.`,
